text: Vladimír Vačkář (born 6 February 1949) is a former Czech cyclist. He competed in the sprint event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Czechoslovakia Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:People from Prostějov
